      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q. How many people we are targeting ?\n---> 20million URL we are generating every day\n\nQ. Example of URL shortener ?\n--->\n\nQ. How small the short URL ?\n---> as short as possible\n\nQ. What characters we can us ?\n---> (0-9, a-z, A-Z)\n\nQ. ",
