      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "QPS (query per second): \n    --> 20 million URLs generated per day. \n    --> write operation: 20 millions / day\n    --> write operation / sec ==> ( 20 * 2^20 ) / 86400 sec ==> ~\n    --> Read operations: \n            asssume, 1:10 (write : read)\n    ---> read operations / sec ==> \n\n ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "QPS (query per second): \n    --> 20 million URLs generated per day. \n    --> write operation: 20 millions / day\n    --> write operation / sec ==> ( 20 * 2^20 ) / 86400 sec ==> ~\n    --> Read operations: \n            asssume, 1:10 (write : read)\n    ---> read operations / sec ==> \n\n ",
