      "locked": false,
      "text": "Storage Unit:\n    (assume for 5years)\n    20 millions urls / day\n    ---> 20 million * 365 days * 5 years = 365 millions records\n    (assume 1 records == 100 byte)\n    ---> 36.5 billions * 100 bytes = 3.65 TB\n\n\n\n",
