      "updated": 1774365689466,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Lets we have a Hash Ring (0-100):\n1. we have DBs.\n    hash(IP of DBs) = 1-100 , and place it into that circle ring.\n2. keys hashing\n    hash(keys) and place into the ring\n3. clocking process\n\n---> Migration is happen, but it will be less\n    \n",
      "fontSize": 53.01609700520831,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Lets we have a Hash Ring (0-100):\n1. we have DBs.\n    hash(IP of DBs) = 1-100 , and place it into that circle ring.\n2. keys hashing\n    hash(keys) and place into the ring\n3. clocking process\n\n---> Migration is happen, but it will be less\n    \n",
