      "updated": 1774367468918,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Limitation:\n    1. Uneven distribution of keys\n        standerd deviation should be Low\n        --> solution:\n                (i) Virtual Nodes (replicas of original nodes) \n                    ---> all virtual nodes have same data. \n                        getting data, that DB will distribute to\n                        other DBs.\n                Slave (virtual DB) and Master (Original DB)\n    2.  Celebrity Problem (hotspot key problem)\n        ---> solution:\n                (i) Virtual Nodes",
      "fontSize": 79.23085821242574,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Limitation:\n    1. Uneven distribution of keys\n        standerd deviation should be Low\n        --> solution:\n                (i) Virtual Nodes (replicas of original nodes) \n                    ---> all virtual nodes have same data. \n                        getting data, that DB will distribute to\n                        other DBs.\n                Slave (virtual DB) and Master (Original DB)\n    2.  Celebrity Problem (hotspot key problem)\n        ---> solution:\n                (i) Virtual Nodes",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
